          <zone h='63281' id='9' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='30760' x='68459' y='29728'>
            <zone h='63281' id='14' name='Price range' w='30760' x='68459' y='29728'>
              <layout-cache minwidth='180' type-h='fixed' type-w='scalable' />
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='13549' id='16' type-v2='text' w='98438' x='781' y='1042'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Player retention varies across game characteristics such as genre, platform features, and pricing. While most games experience declining engagement over time, certain genres and platform features appear more strongly associated with sustained player activity.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='15137' id='17' type-v2='text' w='98438' x='781' y='14591'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Interestingly, completely free games in this dataset show relatively low retention compared with low-priced titles. Games priced in the lower tiers (such as $0–10) appear to maintain player engagement more effectively, suggesting that small purchase costs may be associated with more sustained play.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
