                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='15137' id='17' type-v2='text' w='98438' x='781' y='14591'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Interestingly, completely free games in this dataset show relatively low retention compared with low-priced titles. Games priced in the lower tiers (such as $0–10) appear to maintain player engagement more effectively, suggesting that small purchase costs may be associated with more sustained play.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
